WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.900
Hi, Bodhi.

00:03.900 --> 00:06.400
What polymers are used in packaging?

00:18.100 --> 00:22.100
Common polymers used in packaging
include polyethylene (PE),

00:22.300 --> 00:23.700
polypropylene (PP),

00:23.860 --> 00:25.400
polyethylene terephthalate (PET),

00:25.410 --> 00:27.200
and polystyrene (PS),

00:27.600 --> 00:30.900
chosen for their durability,
flexibility, and barrier properties.
